[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":690},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F":665,"related:\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F":674},"\u002Fen\u002Fjavascript\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F31\u002Fpixijs-v5-38-texturepacker\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":647,"date":648,"description":18,"extension":649,"lang":650,"meta":651,"navigation":257,"path":652,"readingMinutes":653,"seo":654,"standalone":655,"stem":656,"tags":657,"tldr":662,"updated":662,"url":663,"__hash__":664},"content\u002FPixiJS V5 教學\u002FPixiJS V5 教學 (38) - TexturePacker.md","PixiJS V5 教學 (38) - TexturePacker","3727169327",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":640},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,34,37,43,51,56,64,72,75,78,84,87,93,96,99,105,108,114,117,127,130,604,608,611,617,620,636],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"通常來講大多遊戲的素材都會將許多圖片放在一張大圖中，然後透過一個工具去生成 json 減少載入次數。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"texturepacker","TexturePacker",[16,24,25,26,33],{},"TexturePacker 是一款專門為了處理遊戲素材而出現的開發工具，",[27,28,32],"a",{"href":29,"rel":30},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.codeandweb.com\u002Ftexturepacker",[31],"nofollow","下載點在這裡","，TexturePacker 拆解後其實是 Texture(材質) + Packer(打包)，好處是可以將一整張圖檔幫我們會出一個 json 檔案，省下我們自己計算位子等行為。",[16,35,36],{},"下載後我們就可以先打開 TexturePacker (選免費版就好) 然後放置 Play，稍後才會使用",[16,38,39],{},[40,41],"img",{"alt":22,"src":42},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-02-12%2010.07.44.png",[16,44,45,46],{},"接下來在官方網站這裡有提供一個",[27,47,50],{"href":48,"rel":49},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.codeandweb.com\u002Ftexturepacker\u002Ftutorials\u002Fhow-to-create-a-sprite-sheet",[31],"範例圖檔",[16,52,53],{},[40,54],{"alt":50,"src":55},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002FHow_to_create_a_sprite_sheet.png",[16,57,58,59],{},"從官方網站下載的圖檔可能是 .webp 的副檔名，這邊可以使用這個",[27,60,63],{"href":61,"rel":62},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.aconvert.com\u002Ftw\u002Fimage\u002Fwebp-to-png\u002F",[31],"網站來轉換",[16,65,66,67,71],{},"我這邊直接提供我拆開好的",[27,68,50],{"href":69,"rel":70},"https:\u002F\u002Fimgur.com\u002Fa\u002FdysJOn3",[31],"，這樣子等一下才能夠練習。",[12,73,74],{"id":74},"匯入圖檔",[16,76,77],{},"接下來就是要剛剛的連續圖匯入到 TexturePacker，匯入圖檔得方式是點上方 「Add sprites」",[16,79,80],{},[40,81],{"alt":82,"src":83},"Add sprites","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%EF%BC%88%E8%BD%89%EF%BC%89%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8TexturePacker%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%E5%B0%8D%E7%B4%A0%E6%9D%90%E6%89%93%E5%8C%85_-_IT%E9%96%B1%E8%AE%80.png",[16,85,86],{},"然後匯入範例圖檔",[16,88,89],{},[40,90],{"alt":91,"src":92},"匯入全部範例圖檔","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-02-12%2010.44.30.png",[16,94,95],{},"匯入完畢之後其實可以全選整個圖檔，然後按下預覽，你就可以看到圖片會動，我這邊就不展示了。",[16,97,98],{},"接下來就是按下發布精靈表即可，但是這邊建議有一個地方要調整一下，就是右側需要選擇框架，由於我們是使用 PixiJS 所以記得改調整這區塊",[16,100,101],{},[40,102],{"alt":103,"src":104},"轉換成 PixiJS","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2%E4%B8%BA%E6%A1%86%E6%9E%B6.png",[16,106,107],{},"確定沒問題後就按下發布精靈，此時就會生成精靈表（也就是所謂的雪碧圖）以及 json",[16,109,110],{},[40,111],{"alt":112,"src":113},"雪碧圖＆JSON","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FJavaScript\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-02-12%2010.52.26.png",[16,115,116],{},"接下來其他動作就沒有太大的差異，我這邊就不再多介紹程式碼相關直接附上成果(由於 JSON 檔案沒地方只能貼近去 codepen)",[118,119,126],"iframe",{"height":120,"style":121,"scrolling":122,"title":123,"src":124,"frameBorder":122,"allowTransparency":125,"allowFullScreen":125},265,"width: 100%;","no","PIXI TexturePacker Sprite","https:\u002F\u002Fcodepen.io\u002Fhsiangfeng\u002Fembed\u002FdyoYXKw?height=265&theme-id=default&default-tab=js,result","true","\n  See the Pen \u003Ca href='https:\u002F\u002Fcodepe